    "Name": "Nova Cat",
    "Details": "The Blink Cat, dont ask me why its called like that, is a very unusual Refit from the Blood Spirit Clan. Having a Shield is the first thing that Suprises me, considering Shields are nowhere to be seen by Clanners anyway. Next thing is the Unusual weapons loadout, aswell as some Shoulder and Arm Upgrades. As a Whole, this Mech seems not in the Spirit of Clan warfare, but the Blood Spirit Clan were isolationists, so i guess they got it from there.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Extended Torso Twist</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.11</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Omni</color>\n\n",
